{"tid":2062787,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[高地教堂] 希望每個香港人都會識依首歌","createTime":"2020-06-13T11:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T04:24:27.000Z","uid":2634,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d096b4bd071efce38e79e84d89897a169a8509b","tid":2062787,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:34:39.000Z","msg":"除咗《榮光》之外，希望大家可以聽下依首皇家香港警察隊歌、肥彭最鍾意嘅風笛樂曲&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"color: gold;\">Highland Cathedral《高地教堂》</span>，每次聽到首歌都諗到1997 Handover嗰日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，原來仲有人幫首歌配埋中文歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: center;\">\t<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Highland Cathedral 《高地教堂》</span></span><br />\n<br />\n詞：Hans Jurgensmeyer<br />\n<br />\n偉哉香江　我城我等家邦<br />\n傲覽碧海　彪炳戰績輝煌<br />\n仁義禮智　隨伴乘風破浪<br />\n垂範東方　履途挽手逕創<br />\n<br />\n念城邦　立憲遵治道<br />\n歐亞古禮　共冶一爐<br />\n效龍獅　尚智尊道義<br />\n矢勇矢德致志<br />\n<br />\n美哉香江　似洋紫荊茂盛<br />\n耀眼光彩　彰高貴顯尊榮<br />\n苗裔遍世　凝聚同心唱詠<br />\n樂禮鏗鏘　四夷也當謁敬　(重覆)<br />\n<br />\n自由港　未怕海浩瀚<br />\n自強不朽　是我海岸<br />\n太平山　做我等助佑<br />\n敦我克己奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n勇武香港　眾民處變不驚<br />\n盡每分光　光顯社稷威名<br />\n無懼戰鬥　無懼捨生獻命<br />\n榮耀基督　至仁至尊至聖　(重覆)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W25Rv3OCr2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW25Rv3OCr2M&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=40ed60d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W25Rv3OCr2M</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mme1QAAF9ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMme1QAAF9ms&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=42cd4f33\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mme1QAAF9ms</a></div>"},{"pid":"13cd47df81af0a88237700f21886aeec47582a2b","tid":2062787,"uid":2634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"留意返<br />\n《高地教堂》係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"